[Name] HAL-Addon-AppleSMC
[Summary] HAL support for the keyboard light via applesmc.
[Description] The hal-applesmc package, available in the mactel ppa, adds support for keyboard backlight via the applesmc sysfs interface.
[License] Academic Free License version 2.1
[Homepage] http://www.bitmath.org/code/hal-applesmc/
